            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Please upload proof of your Covid-19 Vaccination Status&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
